Task 6 - Category Sales Trend Analysis 2022

Objective
The objective of this task was to compare sales trends across multiple product categories during 2022 and identify category-wise performance patterns using monthly sales analysis.

Tools Used
- Excel

Dataset Features Used
- category
- order_date
- qty_ordered

Analysis Performed
Monthly sales quantities were aggregated category-wise for the year 2022 using pivot table analysis in Excel. Different product categories were compared month-wise to evaluate sales trends, seasonal movement, and category performance variations throughout the year.

Visualization
A time series sales trend chart was created in Excel to visualize monthly category-wise sales performance and compare sales movement across different categories.

Key Insights
The analysis showed noticeable sales trend variations among categories during 2022. Mobiles & Tablets and Home Tech categories demonstrated stronger sales performance during peak months, while smaller categories maintained comparatively lower sales activity.

Files Included
- Excel analysis file
- Sales trend chart
- Insight report
